data.description: Price Reduced by $30K, This beautiful home is located in the Lake Balboa neighborhood, and will make great place for a small family to build beautiful memories. The house has three bedrooms, two bathrooms, with a living room and a kitchen, along with a detached two car garage. There's a lot of room to build an ADU or Just enjoy the spacious backyard for your BBQ parties, there is also a patio. Laundry is located in the kitchen. The house has central air conditioning with the AC unit on the roof. The house is partially off the electric grid with solar panels on the roof, and the new owner can enjoy lower electric bills.
